data.description: PRICE REDUCED!  Turn key unit with brand new wood kitchen topped with beautiful granite and stainless steel appliances.  New laminate flooring downstairs and brand new carpeting throughout rest of townhouse. Entire unit is freshly painted in modern neutral color. Master bedroom has vaulted ceiling with huge walk in closet. Master en suite has stunning tile work in shower along with vanity and granite counter top.  New lighting finishes off this fantastic master suite. Second bedroom has en suite bathroom.  Washer/Dryer upstairs.  NO HOA APPROVAL   CAN RENT IMMEDIATELY *** LET'S MAKE A DEAL***
